C\'e2u 1: Kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c - L\'eanin \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 k\f1\lang1066\u7871? th\u7915?a v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p nh\u7919?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh t\f1\lang1066\u7921?uc\u7911?a:\tab\par
a. Ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng\f1  \par
\f2 b. Ch\f1\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng\par
c. Kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Anh\par
d. Kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? t\u7847?m th\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 2: \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c - L\'eanin l\'e0 g\'ec?\par
a. S\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t c\u7911?a c\u7843?i v\u7853?t ch\u7845?t\par
b. Quan h\u7879? x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i gi\u7919?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i v\u7899?i ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i\par
c. Quan h\u7879? s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t trong m\u7889?i quan h\u7879? t\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng qua l\u7841?i v\u7899?i l\u7921?c l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ki\f1\lang1066\u7871?ntr\f0\lang1033\'fac th\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?ng t\u7847?ng t\f2\u432?\u417?ng \f1\u7913?ng\par
d. Qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t, ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ph\f1\lang1066\u7889?i, trao \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ti\'eau d\'f9ng.\par
C\'e2u 3: Ai l\'e0 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c coi l\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\'e0 kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? th\u7901?i k\u7923? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng th\u7911? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng?\par
a. A. Smith\par
b. D. Ricardoc. \par
W. Pettyd.\par
 R.T.Mathus\par
C\'e2u 4: Ai l\'e0 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c coi l\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\'e1ng l\f1\lang1066\u7853?p ra kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? t\f2\u432? s\f1\u7843?n c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n?\par
a. Smith\par
\f0\lang1033 b. D. Ricardoc. \par
W. Pettyd\par
. R.T.Mathus\par
C\'e2u 5: H\f1\lang1066\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t kinh t\u7871? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a C. M\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c coi l\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\'f2n \f2\'f0\f0\'e1 t\f1\lang1066\u7843?ng trong to\f0\lang1033\'e0n b\f1\lang1066\u7897? h\u7879? th\u7889?ng l\f0\lang1033\'fd lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c - L\'eanin?\par
a. H\f1\lang1066\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?\par
b. H\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? th\u7863?ng d\f2\u432?\par
c. H\f1\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t t\f0\lang1033\'edch l\f2\u361?y t\u432? s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n\par
d. H\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t t\f0\lang1033\'e1i s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t t\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 6: \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7875? nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c - L\'eanin c\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng nhi\u7873?u ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p, ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\'e1p n\'e0o quan tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng nh\u7845?t?\par
a. Tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f0\lang1033\'f3a khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c\par
b. Ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n t\'edch v\'e0 t\f1\lang1066\u7893?ng h\u7907?p\par
c. M\f0\lang1033\'f4 h\'ecnh h\'f3a\par
d. \f2\'d0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u tra th\u7889?ng k\f0\lang1033\'ea\par
C\'e2u 7: Ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a con ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c coi l\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n nh\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\'e0 c\f2\u417? s\f1\lang1066\u7903? c\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i s\u7889?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i?\par
a. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? - x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i\par
b. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t c\u7911?a c\u7843?i v\u7853?t ch\u7845?t\par
c. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng khoa h\u7885?c\par
d. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c, \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 8: Ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? th\u7889?ng nh\u7845?t c\u7911?a:\par
a. T\u7891?n t\u7841?i x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \'fd th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i\par
b. C\f2\u417? s\f1\u7903? h\u7841? t\u7847?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ki\f1\lang1066\u7871?n tr\f0\lang1033\'fac th\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?ng t\u7847?ng\par
c. L\u7921?c l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 quan h\f1\lang1066\u7879? s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t\par
d. C\f2\u417? c\f1\u7845?u kinh t\u7871? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 k\f1\lang1066\u7871?t c\u7845?u giai c\u7845?p x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 9: Quan h\f1\lang1066\u7879? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o gi\f1\lang1066\u7919? vai tr\f0\lang1033\'f2 quy\f1\lang1066\u7871?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh trong quan h\u7879? s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t?\par
a. Quan h\u7879? s\u7903? h\u7919?u v\u7873? t\f2\u432? li\f1\u7879?u s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t\par
b. Quan h\u7879? ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ph\f1\lang1066\u7889?i s\u7843?n ph\u7849?m\par
c. Quan h\u7879? t\u7893? ch\u7913?c qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd\par
d. Kh\'f4ng quan h\f1\lang1066\u7879? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o quy\f1\lang1066\u7871?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh\par
\f0\lang1033 C\'e2u 10: Trong th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y nay, l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t bao g\u7891?m c\f0\lang1033\'e1c y\f1\lang1066\u7871?u t\u7889? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
a. Ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng\par
b. T\f2\u432? li\f1\u7879?u s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t\par
c. Khoa h\u7885?c c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ngh\f1\lang1066\u7879?\par
d. T\u7845?t c\u7843? b\u7885?n tr\f0\lang1033\'ean kia\par
C\'e2u 11. Thu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t ng\u7919? "kinh t\u7871?- ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?" \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng l\u7847?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u ti\f0\lang1033\'ean v\'e0o n\f2\'e3m n\f0\'e0o?\par
a. 1610\par
b. 1612\par
c. 1615\par
d. 1618\par
C\'e2u 12. Ai l\'e0 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u ti\f0\lang1033\'ean \f2\'f0\u432?a ra kh\f0\'e1i ni\f1\lang1066\u7879?m "kinh t\u7871?- ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?"?\par
a. Antoine Montchreti\f0\lang1033\'ean\par
b. Francois Quesney\par
c. Tomas Mun\par
d. William Petty\par
C\'e2u 13: Ricardo l\'e0 nh\'e0 kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? c\u7911?a th\u7901?i k\u7923? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
a. Th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i k\u7923? t\f0\lang1033\'edch lu\f1\lang1066\u7929? nguy\f0\lang1033\'ean thu\f1\lang1066\u7927? TBCN\par
b. Th\u7901?i k\u7923? hi\u7879?p t\f0\lang1033\'e1c gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?n \f2\'f0\u417?n\par
c. Th\f1\u7901?i k\u7923? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng th\u7911? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng\par
d. Th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i k\u7923? \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p c\f2\u417? kh\f0\lang1033\'ed\par
C\'e2u 14: H\'e3y ch\f1\lang1066\u7885?n ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng \f0\lang1033\'e1n \f2\'f0\f0\'fang v\f1\lang1066\u7873? \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?m c\u7911?a quy lu\u7853?t kinh t\u7871?:\par
a. Mang t\f0\lang1033\'ednh kh\'e1ch quan\par
b. Mang t\'ednh ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? quan\par
c. Ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t huy t\'e1c d\f1\lang1066\u7909?ng th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng qua ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng kinh t\u7871? c\u7911?a con ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i\par
d. C\u7843? a v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\par
C\'e2u 15. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7875? nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c L\'eanin c\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng nhi\u7873?uph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p, ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\'e1p n\'e0o quan tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng nh\u7845?t?\par
a. Tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f0\lang1033\'f3a khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c\par
b. Ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n t\'edch v\'e0 t\f1\lang1066\u7893?ng h\u7907?p\par
c. M\f0\lang1033\'f4 h\'ecnh ho\'e1\par
d. \f2\'d0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u tra th\u7889?ng k\f0\lang1033\'ea\par
C\'e2u 16: Khi nghi\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\u7913?c s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t TBCN, C.M\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\f1\lang1066\u7855?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u t\u7915?:\par
a. S\u7843?n xu\u7845?t c\u7911?a c\u7843?i v\u7853?t ch\u7845?t\par
b. L\f2\u432?u th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0ng ho\'e1\par
c. S\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? th\u7863?ng d\f2\u432?\par
d. S\f1\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1 gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?n \f2\'f0\u417?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\'e0ng ho\'e1\par
C\'e2u 17: Tr\f1\lang1066\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f0\lang1033\'f3a khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0:\par
a. G\f1\lang1066\u7841?t b\u7887? nh\u7919?ng b\u7897? ph\u7853?n ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p c\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u.\par
b. G\u7841?t b\u7887? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng ng\u7851?u nhi\f0\lang1033\'ean, b\f1\lang1066\u7873? ngo\f0\lang1033\'e0i, ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? gi\u7919? l\u7841?i nh\u7919?ng m\u7889?i li\f0\lang1033\'ean h\f1\lang1066\u7879? ph\u7893? bi\u7871?n mang t\f0\lang1033\'ednh b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n ch\u7845?t.\par
c. Qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh \f2\'f0i t\f1\lang1066\u7915? c\u7909? th\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c l\u7841?i.\par
d. C\u7843? b v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\par
C\'e2u 18: Ch\f1\lang1066\u7913?c n\f2\'e3ng nh\f1\u7853?n th\u7913?c c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? l\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7857?m:\par
a. Ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n b\u7843?n ch\u7845?t c\u7911?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871?.\par
b. S\u7921? t\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng gi\u7919?a quan h\u7879? s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t v\u7899?i l\u7921?c l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ki\f1\lang1066\u7871?ntr\f0\lang1033\'fac th\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?ng t\u7847?ng.\par
c. T\f0\lang1033\'ecm ra c\'e1c quy lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t kinh t\u7871?\par
d. C\u7843? a, b, c\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 19: Ch\f1\lang1066\u7913?c n\f2\'e3ng ph\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c L\'eanin th\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7879?n \u7903?:\par
a. Trang b\u7883? ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? xem x\f0\lang1033\'e9t th\f1\lang1066\u7871? gi\u7899?i n\f0\lang1033\'f3i chung\par
b. L\'e0 n\f1\lang1066\u7873?n t\u7843?ng l\f0\lang1033\'fd lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c kinh t\u7871? ng\f0\lang1033\'e0nh\par
c. L\'e0 c\f2\u417? s\f1\lang1066\u7903? l\f0\lang1033\'fd lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c n\u7857?m gi\f0\lang1033\'e1p ranh gi\f1\lang1066\u7919?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c tri th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ng\'e0nh kh\'e1c nhau.\par
d. C\f1\lang1066\u7843? b v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\par
C\'e2u 20: Ch\f1\lang1066\u7913?c n\f2\'e3ng t\u432? t\u432?\f1\u7903?ng c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c L\'eanin th\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7879?n \u7903?:\par
a. G\f0\lang1033\'f3p ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng th\u7871? gi\u7899?i quan c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch m\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng c\u7911?a giai c\u7845?p c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nh\'e2n\par
b. T\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ni\u7873?m tin v\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\f1\lang1066\u7855?ng l\u7907?i trong cu\u7897?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7845?u tranh x\f0\lang1033\'f3a b\f1\lang1066\u7887? \f0\lang1033\'e1p b\f1\lang1066\u7913?c b\f0\lang1033\'f3c l\f1\lang1066\u7897?t\par
c. L\f0\lang1033\'e0 v\f2\u361? kh\f0\'ed t\f2\u432? t\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7903?ng c\u7911?a giai c\u7845?p c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nh\'e2n v\'e0 nh\'e2n d\'e2n lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng trong c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng cu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2yd\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng CNXH\par
d. C\u7843? a, b v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\par
C\'e2u 21: B\f1\lang1066\u7843?n ch\u7845?t khoa h\u7885?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'e1ch m\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c L\'eaninth\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7879?n \u7903? ch\u7913?c n\f2\'e3ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
a. Nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?n th\u7913?c\par
b. T\f2\u432? t\u432?\f1\u7903?ng\par
c. Ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n\par
d. C\u7843? a, b v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\par
C\'e2u 22: Ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a con ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c coi l\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n nh\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\'e0 c\f2\u417? s\f1\lang1066\u7903? c\u7911?a\f2\'f0\f1\u7901?i s\u7889?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i?\par
a. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?\par
b. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng khoa h\u7885?c ch\u7845?t\par
c. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t c\u7911?a c\u7843?i v\u7853?t ch\u7845?t\par
d. Ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng ngh\u7879? thu\u7853?t, th\u7875? thao\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 23: \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7875? xem x\f0\lang1033\'e9t, gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?i th\f0\lang1033\'edch ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n g\u7889?c s\f0\lang1033\'e2u xa c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng kinh t\u7871? x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i ph\u7843?i xu\u7845?t ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t t\f1\lang1066\u7915?:\par
a. T\u7915? h\u7879? t\f2\u432? t\u432?\f1\u7903?ng c\u7911?a giai c\u7845?p th\u7889?ng tr\u7883?\par
b. T\u7915? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ho\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng kinh t\u7871?\par
c. T\u7915? truy\u7873?n th\u7889?ng l\u7883?ch s\u7917?\par
d. T\u7915? \f0\lang1033\'fd th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 24: Qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? k\u7871?t h\u7907?p c\u7911?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c y\f1\lang1066\u7871?u t\u7889?:\par
a. S\u7913?c lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\u7899?i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7909? lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng\par
b. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\u7899?i t\f2\u432? li\f1\u7879?u lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng\par
c. S\u7913?c lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\u7899?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\f2\u432? li\f1\lang1066\u7879?u lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng\par
d. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\u7899?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\f2\u432? li\f1\lang1066\u7879?u lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 25: "Nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng th\u7901?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i kinh t\u7871? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c nhau kh\'f4ng ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i \u7903? ch\u7895? ch\f0\lang1033\'fang s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t ra c\f0\lang1033\'e1i g\'ec, m\'e0 l\'e0\f1\lang1066\u7903? ch\u7895? ch\f0\lang1033\'fang s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t b\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch n\'e0o, v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i nh\u7919?ng t\f2\u432? li\f1\u7879?u lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0o". C\'e2u n\'f3i tr\'ean l\'e0 c\f1\lang1066\u7911?aai?\par
a. A. Smith\par
b. D.Ricardo\par
c. C.M\f0\lang1033\'e1c\par
d. Ph.\f2\'c3ng ghen\par
C\f0\'e2u 1. Thu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t ng\u7919? khoa h\u7885?c \f3\ldblquote\f1 kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?\f3\rdblquote  \f1 xu\u7845?t hi\u7879?n l\u7847?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u ti\f0\lang1033\'ean v\'e0o n\f2\'e3m n\f0\'e0o?\par
A. 1610\par
B. 1615\par
C. 1612\par
D. 1618\par
C\'e2u 2. T\'e1c ph\f1\lang1066\u7849?m Chuy\f0\lang1033\'ean lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n v\u7873? Kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7911?a t\f0\lang1033\'e1c gi\f1\lang1066\u7843? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. Antoine de Montchr\'e9tien\par
B. William Stafford\par
C. William Petty\par
D. Thomas Mun\par
C\'e2u 3. Kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c tr\u7903? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t m\f0\lang1033\'f4n khoa h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. Th\f1\lang1066\u7871? k\u7881? XVI\par
B. Th\u7871? k\u7881? XVII\par
C. Th\u7871? k\u7881? XVIII\par
D. Th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX \par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 4. Tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1i n\'e0o \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c ghi nh\u7853?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\f1\lang1066\u7879? th\u7889?ng l\f0\lang1033\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? b\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u v\u7873? n\u7873?n s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t t\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a?\par
A. Tr\u432?\f1\u7901?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1i tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng ti\u7873?n\par
B. Ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng\par
C. Ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng\par
D. Kinh t\f1\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? t\f2\u432? s\f1\u7843?n c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n \u7903? Anh\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 5. Ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng ra \'f0\f1\u7901?i trong th\u7901?i k\f0\lang1033\'ec\par
A. t\'edch lu\f1\lang1066\u7929? t\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n.\par
B. t\f0\lang1033\'edch lu\f1\lang1066\u7929? nguy\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f1\lang1066\u7911?y t\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a.\par
C. ch\f1\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a t\u432? b\f1\u7843?n t\u7921? do c\u7841?nh tranh.\par
D. ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a t\u432? b\f1\u7843?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?c quy\u7873?n.\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 6. \'dd ngh\f2\u297?a c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a t\f2\u432? t\u432?\f1\u7903?ng kinh t\u7871? c\u7911?a ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 g\'ec?\par
A. Ph\'e1t hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n ra quy lu\u7853?t kinh t\u7871?\par
B. \f0\lang1033\'c1p d\f1\lang1066\u7909?ng quy lu\u7853?t kinh t\u7871?\par
C. Ch\f2\u432?a ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n quy lu\u7853?t kinh t\u7871? \f0\lang1033 hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p\par
D. D\u7883?ch v\u7909?\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 9. Ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng l\'e0 h\f1\lang1066\u7879? th\u7889?ng l\f0\lang1033\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? \f2\'f0i s\f0\lang1033\'e2u v\'e0o nghi\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e2nt\'edch \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? r\f0\lang1033\'fat ra l\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? t\u7915? l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. N\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p\par
B. C\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p \par
C. Ngo\u7841?i th\f2\u432?\u417?ng \par
D. D\f1\u7883?ch v\u7909?\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 10. Kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? t\f2\u432? s\f1\u7843?n c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Anh h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\'e0nh v\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. Cu\f1\lang1066\u7889?i th\u7871? k\u7881? XVI \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n n\u7917?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XVII\par
 B. Cu\u7889?i th\u7871? k\u7881? XVII \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n n\u7917?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XVIII\par
C. Cu\u7889?i th\u7871? k\u7881? XVIII \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n n\u7917?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX\par
D. Cu\u7889?i th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n n\u7917?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XX\par
\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 11. W. Petty l\'e0 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i s\f0\lang1033\'e1ng l\f1\lang1066\u7853?p ra tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1i\par
A. ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng.\par
B. kinh t\f1\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p.\par
C. kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Anh.\par
D. kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? ti\u7875?u t\f2\u432? s\f1\u7843?n.\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 12. C. M\'e1c \f2\'f0\f0\'e1nh gi\'e1 ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i s\f0\lang1033\'e1ng l\f1\lang1066\u7853?p ra kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Anh l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ai?\par
A. William Petty\par
B. Adam Smith\par
C. David Ricardo\par
D. Thomas Malthus\par
C\'e2u 13. L\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7911?a C. M\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c k\u7871? th\u7915?a v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p th\f0\lang1033\'e0nht\f1\lang1066\u7921?u c\u7911?a\par
A. ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng.\par
B. ch\f1\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng.\par
C. kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n \u7903? Anh.\par
D. kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? ti\u7875?u t\f2\u432? s\f1\u7843?n.\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 14. L\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7911?a C. M\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\'e0 Ph. \f2\'c3ngghen \'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c th\u7875? hi\u7879?n t\u7853?p trung v\f0\lang1033\'e0c\'f4 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng nh\u7845?t trong t\f0\lang1033\'e1c ph\f1\lang1066\u7849?m n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. B\f1\lang1066\u7843?n th\u7843?o kinh t\u7871?\par
B. T\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n\par
C. H\u7879? t\f2\u432? t\u432?\f1\u7903?ng \f2\'d0\f1\u7913?c\par
D. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0m thu\'ea v\'e0 t\f2\u432? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n \par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 15. H\f1\lang1066\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0o gi\f1\lang1066\u7919? v\u7883? tr\f0\lang1033\'ed l\'e0 h\'f2n \f2\'f0\f0\'e1 t\f1\lang1066\u7843?ng trong to\f0\lang1033\'e0n b\f1\lang1066\u7897? l\f0\lang1033\'ed lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?n kinh t\u7871? c\u7911?a C. M\f0\lang1033\'e1c\par
A. H\f1\lang1066\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? th\u7863?ng d\f2\u432?\par
B. H\f1\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t t\f0\lang1033\'edch lu\f1\lang1066\u7929?\par
 C. H\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?\par
D. H\u7885?c thuy\u7871?t tu\u7847?n ho\f0\lang1033\'e0n v\'e0 chu chuy\f1\lang1066\u7875?n t\f2\u432? b\f1\u7843?n \par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 16. Kinh t\f1\lang1066\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? M\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f3\endash  L\f0\'eanin b\f1\lang1066\u7855?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0o th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. T\f1\lang1066\u7915? \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX\par
B. T\u7915? gi\u7919?a th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX\par
C. T\u7915? cu\u7889?i th\u7871? k\u7881? XIX\par
D. T\u7915? \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u th\u7871? k\u7881? XX\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 17. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u c\u7911?a ch\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng th\f2\u432?\u417?ng thu\f1\u7897?c l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. L\f2\u432?u th\f0\'f4ng\par
B. S\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t\par
C. Ti\u7873?n t\u7879?\par
D. D\u7883?ch v\u7909?\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 18. Ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? ngh\f2\u297?a tr\f1\u7885?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f3 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u thu\u7897?c l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c\par
A. n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p\par
.B. th\f2\u432?\u417?ng nghi\f1\u7879?p.\par
D. d\u7883?ch v\u7909?.\par
C. c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p. \par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 19. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u c\u7911?a kinh t\u7871? ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7893? \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?n Anh l\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'e1c quan h\f1\lang1066\u7879? kinh t\u7871?trong l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c n\f0\lang1033\'e0o?\par
A. S\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t\par
B. L\f2\u432?u th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng\par
\f1\lang1066 B. gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1.C. gi\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? trao \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i c\u7911?a h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1.D. gi\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7843? bi\u7879?t c\u7911?a h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1. C\'e2u 46. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng c\u7909? th\u7875? ph\u7843?n \f0\lang1033\'e1nh t\'ednh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1?A. V\f2\u297?nh vi\f1\lang1066\u7877?nB. X\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?iC. L\u7883?ch s\u7917?D. T\f2\u432? nh\f0\lang1033\'e2nC\'e2u 47. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 g\'ec?A. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng c\u7909? th\u7875? c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1 kh\'f4ng k\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\u7909? th\u7875? c\u7911?a n\f0\lang1033\'f3.B. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1, kh\'f4ng k\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\u7909? th\u7875? c\u7911?an\f0\lang1033\'f3.C. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1 bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1, kh\'f4ng k\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\u7909? th\u7875? c\u7911?an\f0\lang1033\'f3. D. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1 kh\'f4ng k\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\u7909?th\u7875? c\u7911?a n\f0\lang1033\'f3, \f2\'f0\f0\'f3 l\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? hao ph\f0\lang1033\'ed s\f1\lang1066\u7913?c lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1 v\f1\lang1066\u7873? c\f2\u417? b\f1\u7855?p, th\u7847?nkinh, tr\f0\lang1033\'ed \'f3c.C\'e2u 48. Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n g\u7889?c c\u7911?aA. c\u7911?a c\u7843?i.B. gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?.C. gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? trao \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i.D. gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\f0\lang1033\'e1 bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t.C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 49: Gi\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? c\u7911?a h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1 \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c x\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh b\u7903?iA. lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng c\u7909? th\u7875?.B. lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p.C. lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng gi\u7843?n \f2\'f0\u417?n.D. lao \'f0\f1\u7897?ng tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng.\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 50: Lao \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng ph\u7843?n \f0\lang1033\'e1nh t\'ednh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1?A. V\f2\u297?nh vi\f1\lang1066\u7877?nB. X\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?iC. L\u7883?ch s\u7917?D. T\f2\u432? nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n\par
\f1\lang1066 C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 114. Ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t kinh doanh th\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng xuy\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7843?i ti\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'e1y m\'f3c v\'e0 n\'e2ng cao tr\'ecnh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897? chuy\f0\lang1033\'ean m\'f4n cho ng\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng, \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u n\f0\lang1033\'e0y th\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7879?n A. k\f0\lang1033\'edch th\'edch l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n.B. khai th\f0\lang1033\'e1c t\f1\lang1066\u7889?i \f2\'f0a m\f1\u7885?i ngu\u7891?n l\u7921?c c\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7845?t n\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c. C. th\f0\lang1033\'fac \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7849?y t\f2\'e3ng tr\u432?\f1\u7903?ng kinh t\u7871?, h\u7897?i nh\u7853?p kinh t\u7871? qu\u7889?c t\u7871?,D. g\f0\lang1033\'f3p ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n \u7893?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh th\u7883? tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1.C\'e2u 115. Nguy\'ean nh\'e2n d\f1\lang1066\u7851?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n c\u7841?nh tranh trong s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\f2\u432?u th\f0\'f4ng h\'e0ng ho\'e1 xu\f1\lang1066\u7845?t ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t t\f1\lang1066\u7915? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e2u?A. S\f1\lang1066\u7921? t\u7891?n t\u7841?i nhi\u7873?u ch\u7911? s\u7903? h\u7919?uB. S\u7921? gia t\f2\'e3ng s\f1\u7843?n xu\u7845?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\'e1C. Ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n lao \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng d\u7891?i d\f0\lang1033\'e0o trong x\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?iD. S\u7921? thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i cung c\u7847?uC\f0\lang1033\'e2u 116. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7875? ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t c\u7841?nh tranh l\f0\lang1033\'e0nh m\f1\lang1066\u7841?nh v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\f1\lang1066\u7841?nh tranh kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng l\'e0nh m\f1\lang1066\u7841?nh c\u7847?n d\u7921?a v\f0\lang1033\'e0o nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng ti\f0\lang1033\'eau ch\'ed A. t\'ednh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7841?o \f2\'f0\f1\u7913?c, t\f0\lang1033\'ednh ph\'e1p lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t.B. t\f0\lang1033\'ednh truy\f1\lang1066\u7873?n th\u7889?ng, t\f0\lang1033\'ednh nh\'e2n v\f2\'e3n, C, t\f0\'ednh hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i, t\f0\lang1033\'ednh ph\'e1p lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t.D, t\f0\lang1033\'ednh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7841?o \f2\'f0\f1\u7913?c, t\f0\lang1033\'ednh nh\'e2n v\f2\'e3n.C\f0\'e2u 117. M\f1\lang1066\u7897?t trong nh\u7919?ng m\u7863?t h\u7841?n ch\u7871? c\u7911?a c\u7841?nh tranh l\f0\lang1033\'e0 A. L\'e0m cho cung l\f1\lang1066\u7899?n h\f2\u417?n c\f1\u7847?uB. G\f0\lang1033\'e2y t\f1\lang1066\u7893?n h\u7841?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'f4i tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng kinh doanh C. Ti\u7873?n gi\u7845?y khan hi\u7871?m tr\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f1\lang1066\u7883? tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ngD. G\f0\lang1033\'e2y ra hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\u7841?m ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t(Khi th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n c\u7841?nh tranh thi\u7871?u l\f0\lang1033\'e0nh m\f1\lang1066\u7841?nh, c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? d\u7851?n t\u7899?i c\f0\lang1033\'e1c t\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng ti\f0\lang1033\'eau c\f1\lang1066\u7921?c nh\f2\u432?: g\f0\lang1033\'e2y t\f1\lang1066\u7893?n h\u7841?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'f4i tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng kinh doanh, g\f0\lang1033\'e2y l\'e3ng ph\'ed ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n l\u7921?c x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i, l\f0\lang1033\'e0m t\f1\lang1066\u7893?n h\u7841?i ph\f0\lang1033\'fac l\f1\lang1066\u7907?i c\u7911?a x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i.)C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 118. M\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng di \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng A khuy\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'e3i gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?m 50% gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? th\u7867? n\u7841?p, m\u7897?t tu\u7847?n sau m\u7841?ng di \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng B v\f0\lang1033\'e0 C c\f2\u361?ng \'f0\u432?a ra ch\u432?\u417?ng tr\f0\'ecnh khuy\f1\lang1066\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'e3i t\f2\u432?\u417?ng t\f1\lang1066\u7921?. Hi\u7879?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0y ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?n \f0\lang1033\'e1nh quy lu\f1\lang1066\u7853?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a th\u7883? tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng?\par
A. Quy lu\u7853?t cung - c\u7847?uB. Quy lu\u7853?t c\u7841?nh tranhC. Quy lu\u7853?t l\f2\u432?u th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ti\f1\lang1066\u7873?n t\u7879?D. Quy lu\u7853?t gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883?\par
C. \f2\'d0\f1\u7849?y m\u7841?nh c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p ho\f0\lang1033\'e1, hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i ho\f0\lang1033\'e1 n\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p, n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng th\'f4nD. Ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c bi\u7879?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c ch\u7845?t l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng cao C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 48. N\f1\lang1066\u7897?i dung n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\'f3 vai tr\'f2 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c bi\u7879?t quan tr\u7885?ng trong qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p ho\f0\lang1033\'e1, hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i ho\f0\lang1033\'e1 \f1\lang1066\u7903? Vi\u7879?t Nam \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? th\f0\lang1033\'edch \f1\lang1066\u7913?ng v\u7899?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng c\u7911?a cu\u7897?c C\f0\lang1033\'e1ch m\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p l\u7847?n th\u7913? t\f2\u432?A. Ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c bi\u7879?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c ch\u7845?t l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng cao B. Th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n chuy\u7875?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i s\u7889? n\u7873?n kinh t\u7871? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 qu\f1\lang1066\u7843?n tr\u7883? x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?iC. X\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n h\u7841? t\u7847?ng k\f2\u297? thu\f1\u7853?t v\u7873? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ngh\f1\lang1066\u7879? th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin v\'e0 truy\f1\lang1066\u7873?n th\f0\lang1033\'f4ngD. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7849?y m\u7841?nh c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p ho\f0\lang1033\'e1, hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i ho\f0\lang1033\'e1 n\'f4ng nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p, n\f0\lang1033\'f4ng th\'f4n C\'e2u 49. M\f1\lang1066\u7897?t trong nh\u7919?ng gi\u7843?i ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n n\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c ta c\u7847?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? n\f0\lang1033\'e2ng cao tr\'ecnh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o, s\u7917? d\u7909?ng nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c, nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n t\'e0i l\'e0A. \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i m\u7899?i m\u7841?nh m\u7869? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7891?ng b\u7897? l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f3\endash  \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o theo h\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?ng coi tr\u7885?ng ch\u7845?t l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng, hi\u7879?u qu\u7843? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 coi tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng trang b\u7883? n\u7897?i dung ki\u7871?n th\u7913?c cho ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i h\u7885?c. B. quy ho\u7841?ch l\u7841?i m\u7841?ng l\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?i c\f2\u417? s\f1\u7903? gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c ngh\u7873? nghi\u7879?p, gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i h\u7885?c g\u7855?n v\u7899?i quy ho\u7841?ch ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n kinh t\u7871? - x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c. C. th\u7855?t ch\u7863?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u t\f2\u432? cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c bi\u7879?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?u t\f2\u432? cho l\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f3\emdash  \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o. D. t\u7893? ch\u7913?c nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u khoa h\u7885?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f0\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ph\u7843?i thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i c\f2\u417? b\f0\lang1033\'e0n ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c ho\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng, t\f0\lang1033\'e1ch r\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gi\u7919?a nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u, \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o v\u7899?i doanh nghi\u7879?p.C\f0\lang1033\'e2u 50. N\f1\lang1066\u7897?i dung n\f0\lang1033\'e0o d\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?i \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?i ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n n\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c ta c\u7847?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? n\f0\lang1033\'e2ng cao tr\'ecnh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o, s\u7917? d\u7909?ng nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c, nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n t\'e0i?A. \f2\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i m\u7899?i m\u7841?nh m\u7869? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7891?ng b\u7897? l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f3\endash  \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o theo h\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?ng coi tr\u7885?ng ch\u7845?t l\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng,hi\u7879?u qu\u7843? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 coi tr\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ph\u7849?m ch\u7845?t, n\f2\'e3ng l\f1\u7921?c c\u7911?a ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i h\u7885?c B. Quy ho\u7841?ch l\u7841?i m\u7841?ng l\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?i c\f2\u417? s\f1\u7903? gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c ngh\u7873? nghi\u7879?p, gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o d\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i h\u7885?c g\u7855?n v\u7899?i quy ho\u7841?ch ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n kinh t\u7871?, x\f0\lang1033\'e3 h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?cC. T\f2\'e3ng c\u432?\f1\u7901?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u t\f2\u432? cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n ngu\u7891?n nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n l\f1\lang1066\u7921?c, tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p nh\u7845?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?u t\u7915? cho l\f2\u297?nh v\f1\u7921?c gi\f0\lang1033\'e1od\f1\lang1066\u7909?c \f3\endash  \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?oD. T\u7893? ch\u7913?c nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u khoa h\u7885?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f0\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ph\u7843?i thay \f2\'f0\f1\u7893?i c\f2\u417? b\f1\u7843?n ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng ho\f1\u7841?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng, t\f0\lang1033\'e1ch r\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gi\u7919?a nghi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7913?u, \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o v\u7899?i doanh nghi\u7879?p\f0\lang1033\par
}
␀